  "body": "# Problem\n\nWe can't seem to achieve the desired outcome using elevation values on Android's bottom tab bar, this might be acceptable in light mode but makes the shadow completely unnoticeable in dark mode.\n\n## Implementation\n\n1. Disable elevation on Tab Bar on Android\n2. Add a 1px divider, Light Grey (and dark theme equivalent), aligned to the top of the Top Bar, width equals Top Bar width.\n\n<img width=\"683\" alt=\"Screenshot 2020-05-07 at 15 49 29\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4932774/81302202-584be480-907a-11ea-931d-58838640c888.png\">\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\nElevation is replaced by a divider\n\n## Notes\n\nElevation can suck a donkey ball",
